Package com.msasc.lib.json

Class JSONObject

java.lang.Object
com.msasc.lib.json.JSONObject
public class JSONObject extends Object
A JSON object is an ordered collection of name/value pairs, externally represented as a string formatted following the ECMA-404 specification.
Author:
Miquel Sas
